Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉宫学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.36,0:00:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.39,0:00:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前就一直很喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请跟我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.85,0:01:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.53,0:03:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 原来是千鹤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吓唬人家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又甩人啦 这个月已经是第几个了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 别逗我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下 等一下我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个男生是男子游泳部的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他为什么会跟你表白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛...因为喜欢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这问题你问他好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有啊 你这口吻 说得好像我一点魅力都没有似的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜对人家一无所知哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们还认为表白会成功吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:03:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 也有这个可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像把交往看得很随便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.92,0:04:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想说“交往了就应该结婚”吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤你太守旧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没说到这份上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你那明显“随便玩玩”的心态 我可不敢苟同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“随便玩玩”...你会不会说得太过了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 根据千鹤的理论
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不先了解好对方 就不能表白了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 凡事都有个顺序
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相识 相知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在深刻了解对方之后 才最后表白心迹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点可是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算“光荣牺牲”也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是能传达自己的心意给对方 那就很满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种不是单纯的自我满足吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不顾虑对方的思念 肯定是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是因为老这么说 才交不到男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,样样都按着顺序来 少女都变老太婆了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:05:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜你自己到头来不也是跟谁都没好上过嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嘛 又没你那种坚信不疑的理由呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你想说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了第二学期 茜你就变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像变回刚进白棱那时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.97,0:05:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 亏你还记得这么清楚呢 都咸丰年间的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.41,0:05:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡过头 然后迟到 学习也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样 只有自信比别人多一倍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想忘也忘不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现 现在我才不是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这份阳光气息跟那时一样 晶莹通透啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 你是诗人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 去美国留学那事进展得怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是英语什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...一般般吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这表情是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚入学的时候 英语不是糟透顶嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点还是跟以前一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 坏心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 饿死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快淋个澡换身衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会先准备好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.37,0:06:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该在房间里面学习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 鸣海哥有没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没过来 貌似工作很忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他最近都没怎么来 有点点寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.01,0:06:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算“光荣牺牲”也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是能传达自己的心意给对方 那就很满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种不是单纯的自我满足吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不顾虑对方的思念 肯定是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也没来电话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:07:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊 我想着等下去趟图书馆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 最近都不能跟你一起学习
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啦 茜自己也有很多事情要忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留学的准备很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也得加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.11,0:08:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近 鸣海哥都没怎么过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 之前不是天天都过来吗 而且电话也...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.96,0:09:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之说他现在班制换了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才没什么时间过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 电话那方面...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 早
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 早上吃面包？还是吃饭？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃面包好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去泡红茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喝奶茶好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.74,0:09:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 下一句
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁郁相思苦 自甘绝此生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}玉の绪よ　绝えなば绝えね　ながらへば
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苟延人世上 无计掩痴情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}忍ぶることの　弱りもぞする
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs23}(*这句摘自小仓百人一首 第89首)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念这一句的 是平安时代末期的和歌诗人兼王族式子内亲王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 和风汉堡套餐以及炸虾套餐 各一份对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饮料要什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之很卖力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他之前太马虎啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个“时薪小偷”总算醒悟了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长说根据孝之的表现 决定要给他加时薪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的 真由真由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我亲耳听见的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 店长他在想什么啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来他不懂什么叫经营呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点我深感抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.35,0:10:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店 店长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身担店长这个重要使命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给大家添麻烦 我深感抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ha ha ha
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我总算也有了身为店长的自觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也开始形成有自己特色的一套经营理念
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 真可靠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:10:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 真由真由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:11:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,举双手同意 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.15,0:11:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羊毛出在羊身上 哪里增加了再找个地方减掉就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找个地方减掉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道不这么认为吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.39,0:11:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由真由 贵客惠临了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 要先下单再端水给他们才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺序反啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开 屎壳郎 别挡路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长 这可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太宠她们啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.05,0:11:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们啊 可是有阳光就灿烂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有道理 我会注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说这个了 实在不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然拜托你改班制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里 鸣海你能多上几个班 对我来说也是求之不得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福 我们情况乐观多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣海你这边真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 你的私人时间不就没有了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.35,0:12:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会 这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我想努力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那我也没有什么要说的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 屎壳郎 你有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 挑这么忙的时候来 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.02,0:12:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小...茜？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.25,0:12:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉啊 让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 我才是突然间跑到你工作的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不忙了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是休息时间 给
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.28,0:12:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准用敬语 我之前没跟你说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:12:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ha ha ha 给
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗓门还是跟以前一样大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊 我言行不谨慎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 知错就去改吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 今天找我有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥她出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？这是我想问的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:14:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟姐姐之间发生什么事了 鸣海哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不就...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在暂时保持一点距离
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们之前不是还很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前还想 遥她现在很精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能待在她身边 对她有好处
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 看来是我搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事 姐姐她无论什么时候都对鸣海哥...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥才没有这么软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她其实相当坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我这种人 要坚强的多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...就算是也不用...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己男友始终是个自由职业者 会让遥很不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说“要配得起遥”这种说法很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但当我想了想今后的事 就觉得保持现状可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣海哥...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.44,0:15:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥才没有这么软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她其实相当坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我这种人 要坚强得多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“就如夜空中繁星般闪烁”...吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有真心喜欢过一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水月学姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 有什么奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因 因为...那 就算鸣海哥选择了姐姐 你也无所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他也会注视我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？我可没说“你眼中只能有我一个”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是说“希望你也能注视我”罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才说...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜 你有真心喜欢过一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没试过的话 继续说下去也不会有任何意义
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的话 也只是想法不同 仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说着这种话来逃避 我不能允许
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从最开始没想过要你允许
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得鸣海哥很可怜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他哪里可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.39,0:17:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还必须应酬你的鸣海哥的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你 绝对理解不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你 连存在本身都是失常的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我 也有真心喜欢的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么飞机啊 那是我要送的...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么磨蹭谁有闲心等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉宫学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在担心什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我今天想早点走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个 我叫做凉宫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 突然叫你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我帮不上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 为 为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平学长你不是姐姐她们的挚友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挚友啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没听过这个词了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经跟孝之谈过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也听了他的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.07,0:19:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们 还是说“再见”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己决定的 “要跟遥一起活下去”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我能理解 但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仅是为了遥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是为了我的人生 才想这样做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最开始我的确很吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 他还是决定要尊重凉宫的意愿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然孝之跟凉宫之间都发生了不少事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总算能恢复原状 不 总算能迈步向前了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我相信他们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平学长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 抱歉 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉 我马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我 好痛啊 靠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才好像有人在看这边...是我的错觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.84,0:21:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你丫 快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.53,0:21:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“对不起 我不会重犯了” 来 说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱吠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.63,0:21:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少你也说日语啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有反省的意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.74,0:21:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我放
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.66,0:22:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你不对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.69,0:22:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 玉野
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9比1 我认为是前辈的压倒性胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.31,0:22:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 我们干活去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.81,0:22:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领着工资就得好好干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋 给我去踩猫屎吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.79,0:22:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.11,0:22:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 妈妈真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.38,0:22:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.45,0:23:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.74,0:23:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.42,0:23:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸今天可能会比较晚回来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.74,0:23:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.42,0:23:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 妈妈 你做这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.56,0:23:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是习惯了连孝之那份也做了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.05,0:23:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家努力吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.19,0:23:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天孝之不来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.32,0:23:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之也是要工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.04,0:23:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能勉强他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.01,0:23:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.31,0:23:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈我好寂寞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.24,0:23:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他最近好像很忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.28,0:23:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次记得转告他有空随时来家里坐坐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.46,0:23:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.83,0:23:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别骗我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.20,0:23:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？茜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.79,0:23:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你别再骗我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.76,0:23:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗是...指什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.31,0:23:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.93,0:23:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐说要跟鸣海哥分手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.15,0:23:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事 请你好好说明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.54,0:24:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣海哥他这么努力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.03,0:24:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对他有什么不满 你倒是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.22,0:24:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜 要吃晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.93,0:24:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.03,0:24:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是姐姐 你用得着这么娇惯她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.05,0:24:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈你也觉得奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.65,0:24:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.76,0:24:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣海哥之前每天都过来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.61,0:24:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然间就不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.36,0:24:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来每晚都会打个电话过来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.67,0:24:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然间也不打了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.18,0:24:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没察觉到才奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.31,0:24:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜你不会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.16,0:24:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.14,0:24:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我跟孝之的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.56,0:24:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟茜...没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.92,0:24:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系？你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.85,0:24:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏姐姐你还能这么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.40,0:24:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣海哥他干活相当卖力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.96,0:24:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他相信姐姐 想跟姐姐你在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.77,0:24:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了跟姐姐的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.97,0:25:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他这么努力 但不是很可怜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.34,0:25:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要保持距离
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.01,0:25:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是姐姐你自己任性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.84,0:25:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要撒娇撒到什么地步才舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.66,0:25:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜 你明明什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.55,0:25:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.97,0:25:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.74,0:25:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥！